a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of predict \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/predict\">predict</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of prejudice \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/prejudice\">prejudice</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of revenge \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/revenge\">revenge</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of soi-disant \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/soi-disant\">soi-disant</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of syndic \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/syndic\">syndic</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of teach \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/teach\">teach</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of tetchy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/tetchy\">tetchy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theodicy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theodicy\">theodicy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of toe \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/toe\">toe</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of token \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/token\">token</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of valediction \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/valediction\">valediction</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of vendetta \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/vendetta\">vendetta</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of verdict \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/verdict\">verdict</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of veridical \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/veridical\">veridical</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of vindicate \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\"